load/2016/12/20/161000_7e3e39310ab30b20622dd8ef4ca5da02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F161000_7e3e39310ab30b20622dd8ef4ca5da02.jpg&h=982bd756&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n80r% = (1 - r%)*60<br />\n80r% = 60 - 60r%<br />\n80r% + 60r% = 60<br />\n140r% = 60<br />\nr% = 6/14"},{"pid":"3d2370c7785a9a384aa0d0c40560b638be86650e","tid":47244,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>數學好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢條數唔知點計落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打們可唔可以指教下<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/161000_7e3e39310ab30b20622dd8ef4ca5da02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F161000_7e3e39310ab30b20622dd8ef4ca5da02.jpg&h=982bd756&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n80r% = (1 - r%)*60<br />\n80r% = 60 - 60r%<br />\n80r% + 60r% = 60<br />\n140r% = 60<br />\nr% = 6/14</blockquote><br />\nsor睇錯題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32846b2d0645e8a03f12280c436b82532a02bb48","tid":47244,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"r%咪啫係r/100，有幾難計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d27aae0acbf2aa3aff00d5e8af0db982621d2c","tid":47244,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>r%咪啫係r/100，有幾難計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n60次方方程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fb7c49c09dd8c7511005120ddadbc24426bad6","tid":47244,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>數學好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢條數唔知點計落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打們可唔可以指教下<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/161000_7e3e39310ab30b20622dd8ef4ca5da02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F161000_7e3e39310ab30b20622dd8ef4ca5da02.jpg&h=982bd756&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n80r% = (1 - r%)*60<br />\n80r% = 60 - 60r%<br />\n80r% + 60r% = 60<br />\n140r% = 60<br />\nr% = 6/14</blockquote><br />\nsor睇錯題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根據粗略計算 <br />\nr%好似係2.33899<br />\n岩既話先show step啦<br />\n錯就由佢當我無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c536b3656e94d0fed866fba1eb9587bec4561c17","tid":47244,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg&h=b10c5e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係無列錯式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415b85c36e2ff1324889146c71ea28b1e1b462eb","tid":47244,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg&h=b10c5e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係無列錯式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq