Time":"2016-12-20T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"題目呢"},{"pid":"296e378aceefccb547f05b4e21336c26b304d32b","tid":47244,"uid":56752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:30:18.000Z","msg":"如果r 係interest rate既話, 用binomial theorem expands 個60次方expression出黎, 因為higher order terms 會vanish, 拎頭幾個terms可以approximates到個result.<br />\n<br />\n響街寫唔到俾你."},{"pid":"1e5a9f1255882947bdcd7e5580ad8a38548a6dc5","tid":47244,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg&h=b10c5e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係無列錯式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n0.9%正常啦<br />\nBTW 樓上各位叻唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry lo&hellip;<br />\n得部手機係手<br />\n又無紙筆<br />\n邊及得你電腦叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56e870cf68bc29e745f93343e734c6f8f18282a","tid":47244,"uid":26730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg&h=b10c5e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係無列錯式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n0.9%正常啦<br />\nBTW 樓上各位叻唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry lo&hellip;<br />\n得部手機係手<br />\n又無紙筆<br />\n邊及得你電腦叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地都係用手機計 真係柒出國際"},{"pid":"1d250959c3d71b29aa25958227bdc76147ab260c","tid":47244,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果r 係interest rate既話, 用binomial theorem expands 個60次方expression出黎, 因為higher order terms 會vanish, 拎頭幾個terms可以approximates到個result.<br />\n<br />\n響街寫唔到俾你.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係如果個r唔細<br />\n之後high order term 未零到<br />\nOrder 4以上中學都已經solve唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留名學嘢"},{"pid":"4c4804c65e4db131a1941962be646615ddd40982","tid":47244,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n0.9%正常啦<br />\nBTW 樓上各位叻唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry lo&hellip;<br />\n得部手機係手<br />\n又無紙筆<br />\n邊及得你電腦叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地都係用手機計 真係柒出國際</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連60次方方程都睇唔到就衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c0c43bc071e0e4c72c9c7e8a0f64ba12c13438","tid":47244,"uid":35739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg&h=b10c5e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係無列錯式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係0.00935575<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇人知中間個步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係中學 high dip其中一科入面要學time value of money 條式肯定冇錯 只不過唔識拆條式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64806d585157baa8595163e61b8a785efd36bcf4","tid":47244,"uid":56752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果r 係interest rate既話, 用binomial theorem expands 個60次方expression出黎, 因為higher order terms 會vanish, 拎頭幾個terms可以approximates到個result.<br />\n<br />\n響街寫唔到俾你.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係如果個r唔細<br />\n之後high order term 未零到<br />\nOrder 4以上中學都已經solve唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留名學嘢</blockquote><br />\n邊度有講係中學數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我眼殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d192648752d562b89d29119b35ec069c1ac2ad0","tid":47244,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg&h=b10c5e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係無列錯式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係0.00935575<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇人知中間個步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係中學 high dip其中一科入面要學time value of money 條式肯定冇錯 只不過唔識拆條式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 Newton's method<br />\n<br />\nf(x) = (1 + x)^60 - 80x - 1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/52c50eca0b7c4d64ef2fdca678665b73e944cb84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikimedia.org%2Fapi%2Frest_v1%2Fmedia%2Fmath%2Frender%2Fsvg%2F52c50eca0b7c4d64ef2fdca678665b73e944cb84&h=7b0ce499&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37a665579bbf9eeddd30b23e9c961945447778fc","tid":47244,"uid":35739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181339_5fda6e9a96199cf38cee18bb6fc32dac.jpg&h=b10c5e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係無列錯式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係0.00935575<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇人知中間個步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係中學 high dip其中一科入面要學time value of money 條式肯定冇錯 只不過唔識拆條式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 Newton's method<br />\n<br />\nf(x) = (1 + x)^60 - 80x - 1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/52c50eca0b7c4d64ef2fdca678665b73e944cb84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikimedia.org%2Fapi%2Frest_v1%2Fmedia%2Fmath%2Frender%2Fsvg%2F52c50eca0b7c4d64ef2fdca678665b73e944cb84&h=7b0ce499&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打可否列埋之後個步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}